Ecartip Groupe Fondasol, Mastering the ground, support projects…

   Discover Ecartip Groupe Fondasol
     * Topographer
     * Cartography
     * Network detection
     * BIM
     * Lasergrammetry, Photogrammetry
     * Linear Infrastructure Project Execution Studies

Whatever the ground, we’ll be able to support your projects

   Montpellier tram system

   Starting from a soil study, geotechnical investigations, and
   soil-structure interaction modelling, our engineers have appropriate
   solutions for geotechnical problems encountered:
     * Earthworks
     * Stability of your ground
     * Retaining structures
     * Foundations and underpinning
     * Roadways and car-parks
     * Slabs
     * Ground improvement
     * Structures in aquatic sites
     * Managing underground water

Geotechnics at your service

   To optimize your projects, we systematically take all the following
   factors into account:
     * nature and behaviour of the materials,
     * re-use or disposal of the materials,
     * impact on adjoining land and constructions,
     * overall stability of the site,
     * site constraints (topography, compressibility, seismicity, flood
       risk, water table, cavities, history of the site),
     * project constraints (works phasing, loading, superstructure,
       operating constraints).

Type of structure, reference

   FONDASOL’s expertise covers all types of structure:
     * Buildings
     * Public installations
     * Industrial structures
     * Civil engineering
     * Maritime and inland waterway structures
     * Linear infrastructures
     * Natural risks

